---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Leak Detection"
  description={`Professional leak detection services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC. Find and fix even the smallest leaks before they cause water damage. Call ${site.phone}.`}
  heroTitle="Don't Let Leaks Damage Your Home"
  heroSubtitle="Hire us for leak detection services in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-26.jpg"
  listHeading="Interior leaks can lead to:"
  listItems={[
    'Mold and mildew',
    'Increased water bills',
    'Water damage to walls and ceilings',
  ]}
  listNote="Don't wait until it's too late to hire leak detection services. Contact us now to schedule an inspection."
  ctaHeading="Stop That Trickle Before It Becomes a Flood"
>
  <p>
    There are a lot of issues that can cause your pipes to leak, and they can be hard to spot
    until it's too late. That's why the pros at Nesbitt's Plumbing offer prompt, professional
    leak detection services to customers in Hendersonville and Asheville, NC. Our team is trained
    to find even the smallest of leaks and fix them in a timely manner in order to prevent water
    damage to your home.
  </p>
  <p>
    Call <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    today to set up a consultation.
  </p>
  <h2 class="pt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900">
    Stop that trickle before it becomes a flood of costly damage
  </h2>
  <p>
    If left undetected, leaks can cause major damage to your home, from hidden mold growth to
    ruined drywall and rising utility bills. Our trained technicians pinpoint the source quickly
    so repairs stay small and affordable.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
